{"id":289218,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/04/维权网-广东声援刘远东的数位网友被拘留/","date":"2013-04-15T19:31:44Z","modified":"2013-04-15T19:31:44Z","title":"维权网 | 广东声援刘远东的数位网友被拘留","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>（维权网信息员李宁报道）</span>2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>日</span><span>，数位律师和网友证实：广东网友聂光先生，因在东莞和广州年底举牌声援刘远东被治安拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>天。贾榀先生也是因声援刘远东，而被数行为并罚治安拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>天。袁小华先生因为声援和看望贾榀和聂光，被以煽动非法集会罪治安拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>天，陈剑雄先生是因为声援和看望贾榀和聂光被拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>天。</span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">    </span></div>\n<div><span>据吴魁明律师说：他下午跟刘正清律师去东莞会见被拘留的袁小华先生，找了很久，终于找到了关押袁先生的地方，位于大朗的大有园附近的东莞拘留所。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">    </span></div>\n<div><span>吴律师说：交往手续后，他一直等待，却没想到碰到了来见聂光先生的范标文律师。吴律师还说：今天的会见，当局只给了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>分钟。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">    </span></div>\n<div><span>据悉：袁小华、陈剑雄、贾榀、聂光四人都被拘留在东莞大有围拘留所。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-RUb9MRaG_oI/UWwpVgk0GhI/AAAAAAAAgZM/-cGC5vnEkoM/s1600/%E5%A4%A7%E6%98%8E%E5%9B%AD%E6%8B%98%E7%95%99%E6%89%80.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"262\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-RUb9MRaG_oI/UWwpVgk0GhI/AAAAAAAAgZM/-cGC5vnEkoM/s320/%E5%A4%A7%E6%98%8E%E5%9B%AD%E6%8B%98%E7%95%99%E6%89%80.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br />